{"tid":1002501,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸真係好貴","createTime":"2019-01-31T03:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T09:09:47.000Z","uid":164853,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f4ef68167a7304101f3fe51abcc439f85328d6","tid":1002501,"uid":164853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"因壓力同失眠開始爛面<br />\n去睇皮膚專科 佢開抗生素俾我<br />\n一食就食咗半年 <br />\n一個星期咁開$600<br />\n一個月就$2400<br />\n半年就$14400<br />\n<br />\n佢一直都只開抗生素俾我<br />\n每次食完我都期待塊面有好轉<br />\n點知都係咁嘅撚樣<br />\n<br />\n最近又黎料 <br />\n每次照鏡我都想問點解神愛世人 <br />\n但你又要創造暗瘡出黎害世人？<br />\n我終於開口話要食A酸<br />\nO牌20mg 一日兩粒<br />\n一個星期藥+抗生素 $900<br />\n一星期覆診一次<br />\n好撚貴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解人地都係學生哥<br />\n返part time搵嘅錢鍾意買咩就買咩<br />\n我搵返黎嘅錢就要用黎睇醫生<br />\n然而我塊面仍然係咁嘅撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呻完了 想問巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇睇邊個醫生食a酸係平啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5162536ea84979254b5acff759ffa9547d044074","tid":1002501,"uid":46752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"題外話：努力，自己做醫生，慳番她多錢"},{"pid":"6bb05f032c63e725f710d9835142261e1e41a2a7","tid":1002501,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5162536ea84979254b5acff759ffa9547d044074","tid":1002501,"uid":46752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"題外話：努力，自己做醫生，慳番她多錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"5afd2611459adcc069edaead6582ef62f0a8f918","tid":1002501,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"用外用 一個月100蚊<br />\n食omega3抗炎 一日2g 一個月都係百幾蚊"},{"pid":"76b6d53ca86bed12adb91f446f1ce73a28ebd77b","tid":1002501,"uid":164853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"